title: Saints coach Payton expects Brees to start Sunday
text:
> Texas Saints coach Payton expects Brees to start Sunday FILE - In this Sept. 27, 2015, file photo, New Orleans Saints' Drew Brees stretches before an NFL football game against the Carolina Panthers in Charlotte, N.C. Brees is trying to work his way back into the lineup after missing last week's game with a throwing shoulder injury.
